       BN_CTX_new() returns a pointer to the BBNN_CCTTXX. If the
       allocation fails, it returns NNUULLLL and sets an error code
       that can be obtained by ERR_get_error(3).

       BN_CTX_init() and BN_CTX_free() have no return values.

